| physical_plan | BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |   SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |     VirtualExecutionPlan name=SparkConnect compute_context=sc://dbc-f34ee0b7-90f2.cloud.databricks.com:443/;user_id=spice.ai;x-databricks-cluster-id=0711-151224-1rh2uz8m;use_ssl=true sql=SELECT sum(store_sales.ss_net_profit) AS total_sum, store.s_state, store.s_county, (grouping(store.s_state) + grouping(store.s_county)) AS lochierarchy, rank() OVER (PARTITION BY (grouping(store.s_state) + grouping(store.s_county)), CASE WHEN (grouping(store.s_county) = 0) THEN store.s_state END ORDER BY sum(store_sales.ss_net_profit) DESC NULLS FIRST RANGE BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW) AS rank_within_parent FROM store_sales JOIN date_dim AS d1 ON ((d1.d_date_sk = store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk) AND (d1.d_month_seq BETWEEN 1180 AND (1180 + 11))) JOIN store ON ((store.s_store_sk = store_sales.ss_store_sk) AND store.s_state IN (SELECT tmp1.s_state FROM (SELECT store.s_state, rank() OVER (PARTITION BY store.s_state ORDER BY sum(store_sales.ss_net_profit) DESC NULLS FIRST RANGE BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW) AS ranking FROM store_sales JOIN store ON true JOIN date_dim ON true WHERE (((date_dim.d_month_seq BETWEEN 1180 AND (1180 + 11)) AND (date_dim.d_date_sk = store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk)) AND (store.s_store_sk = store_sales.ss_store_sk)) GROUP BY store.s_state) AS tmp1 WHERE (tmp1.ranking <= 5))) GROUP BY ROLLUP (store.s_state, store.s_county) ORDER BY lochierarchy DESC NULLS FIRST, CASE WHEN (lochierarchy = 0) THEN store.s_state END ASC NULLS LAST, rank_within_parent ASC NULLS LAST LIMIT 100 rewritten_sql=SELECT sum(`spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store_sales`.`ss_net_profit`) AS `total_sum`, `spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store`.`s_state`, `spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store`.`s_county`, (grouping(`spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store`.`s_state`) + grouping(`spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store`.`s_county`)) AS `lochierarchy`, rank() OVER (PARTITION BY (grouping(`spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store`.`s_state`) + grouping(`spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store`.`s_county`)), CASE WHEN (grouping(`spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store`.`s_county`) = 0) THEN `spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store`.`s_state` END ORDER BY sum(`spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store_sales`.`ss_net_profit`) DESC NULLS FIRST RANGE BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW) AS `rank_within_parent` FROM `spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store_sales` JOIN `spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`date_dim` AS `d1` ON ((`d1`.`d_date_sk` = `spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store_sales`.`ss_sold_date_sk`) AND (`d1`.`d_month_seq` BETWEEN 1180 AND (1180 + 11))) JOIN `spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store` ON ((`spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store`.`s_store_sk` = `spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store_sales`.`ss_store_sk`) AND `spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store`.`s_state` IN (SELECT `tmp1`.`s_state` FROM (SELECT `spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store`.`s_state`, rank() OVER (PARTITION BY `spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store`.`s_state` ORDER BY sum(`spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store_sales`.`ss_net_profit`) DESC NULLS FIRST RANGE BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW) AS `ranking` FROM `spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store_sales` JOIN `spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store` ON true JOIN `spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`date_dim` ON true WHERE (((`spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`date_dim`.`d_month_seq` BETWEEN 1180 AND (1180 + 11)) AND (`spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`date_dim`.`d_date_sk` = `spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store_sales`.`ss_sold_date_sk`)) AND (`spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store`.`s_store_sk` = `spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store_sales`.`ss_store_sk`)) GROUP BY `spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store`.`s_state`) AS `tmp1` WHERE (`tmp1`.`ranking` <= 5))) GROUP BY ROLLUP (`spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store`.`s_state`, `spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store`.`s_county`) ORDER BY `lochierarchy` DESC NULLS FIRST, CASE WHEN (`lochierarchy` = 0) THEN `spiceai_sandbox`.`tpcds`.`store`.`s_state` END ASC NULLS LAST, `rank_within_parent` ASC NULLS LAST LIMIT 100 |
